1. Binance Wallet will launch Privasea AI (PRAI) TGE on May 14, requiring 198 Alpha points or certain conditions to participate;
2. New on Binance Alpha: Bluefin (BLUE);
3. Analyst: Over $35 billion flowed into the crypto market in the past three weeks;
4. Binance Alpha and contracts will soon launch NEXPACE (NXPC);
5. Binance upgrades designated account plan;
6. Binance will launch NXPC perpetual contracts and leveraged trading;
7. Coincheck financial report: Completed the acquisition of staking platform Next Finance Tech, customer assets increased to $5.732 billion;
8. Binance VIP borrowing adds KMNO, SYRUP, SXT, STO borrowable assets;
9. A whale spent 1.56 million USDT to buy 9.55 million LAUNCHCOIN;
10. Binance's principal-guaranteed earning coin launches LAYER regular product;
11. Bitcoin Magazine CEO: If the BTC price on the company's balance sheet is lower than its value, why not sell and repurchase the shares?
12. A whale sold 341,783 TRUMPs, losing $446,000;
13. Australia's Monochrome spot Bitcoin ETF's holdings rose to 420 BTC;
14. A whale withdrew 72,500 SOL from FalconX and pledged it;
15. The giant whale "silentraven" exchanged 100 WBTC for 3,855.2 ETH.
